<html>
	<head>
		<title>WordPress Plugin Boilerplate Generator | Ready to use WordPress Plugin Boilerplate</title>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<meta name="description" content="WordPress Plugin Boilerplate Generator, Stop wasting time searching and replacing text strings manually" />
		<meta name="keywords" content="WordPress Plugin Boilerplate Generator" />
		<meta property="og:url" content="https://boilerplate.pablocianes.com/" />
		<meta property="og:title" content="WordPress Plugin Boilerplate Generator | Ready to use WordPress Plugin Boilerplate" />
		<meta property="og:image" content="http://wppb.me/images/wppb-share.jpg" />
		<script src="js/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="//cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-form-validator/2.1.47/jquery.form-validator.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/skel.min.js"></script>
		<script src="js/init.js"></script>
		<noscript>
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/skel.css" />
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css" />
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style-wide.css" />
		</noscript>
	</head>
	<body>

		<!-- Header -->
			<div id="header">
				<h1>WordPress Plugin Boilerplate<br> Generator</h1>
				<span class="logo icon fa-plug"></span>
				<h2>'Fork' realizado por <a target="_blank" href="https://pablocianes.com/" title="WordPress Plugin Boilerplate fork by Pablo Cianes">Pablo Cianes</a></h2>
				<h2>basado en el <a target="_blank" href="http://wppb.io/" title="WordPress Plugin Boilerplate by Tom McFarlin">WPPB de Tom McFarlin</a></h2>
				<h3>cuyo mantenimiento cedió a <a target="_blank" href="http://devinvinson.com/">Devin Vinson</a></h3>
				<h3>y sobre el que <a target="_blank" href="https://enriquechavez.co/">Enrique Chavez</a> creo un generador como este</h3>
				<p>No pierdas tiempo al crear tu plugin con este generador de plugins de WordPress<br> en OOP y basado en el trabajo de todas estas personas</p>
			</div>

		<!-- Main -->
			<div id="main">

				<header class="major container 75%">
					<h2>Sólo tienes que indicar
					<br />
					algunos detalles de personalización
					<br />
					y en unos instantes se generará un zip
					<br />
					con todo el código preparado</h2>
				</header>

				<div class="box container">
					<header>
						<h2>Crea tu plugin base en OOP para WordPress</h2>
					</header>
					<section>
						<form method="POST" action="/" id="wppb-form">
							<div class="row">
								<div class="6u 12u(3)">
									<label for="name">Nombre del plugin</label>
									<input class="text" type="text" name="name" id="name" value="" placeholder="Your amazing plugin" data-validation="required" />
								</div>
								<div class="6u 12u(3)">
									<label for="slug">Slug del plugin</label>
									<input class="text" type="text" name="slug" id="slug" value="" placeholder="your-amazing-plugin" data-validation="required" />
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="row">
								<div class="12u">
									<label for="uri">URI del plugin</label>
									<input class="text" type="text" name="uri" id="uri" value="" placeholder="Your Plugin URI" data-validation="required" data-validation="url" />
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="row">
								<div class="6u 12u(3)">
									<label for="author-name">Nombre del autor</label>
									<input class="text" type="text" name="author[name]" id="author-name" value="" placeholder="Your name" data-validation="required" />
								</div>
								<div class="6u 12u(3)">
									<label for="author-email">Email del autor</label>
									<input class="text" type="email" name="author[email]" id="author-email" value="" placeholder="your@email.tld" data-validation="required"  data-validation="email"/>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="row">
								<div class="12u">
									<label for="author-uri">URI del autor</label>
									<input class="text" type="text" name="author[uri]" id="author-uri" value="" placeholder="http://yoursite.tld" data-validation="required" data-validation="url" />
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="row">
								<div class="12u">
									<ul class="actions">
										<li><input type="submit" value="Crear ZIP" /></li>
										<li><input type="reset" value="Borrar" class="alt" /></li>
									</ul>
								</div>
							</div>
						</form>
					</section>
				</div>
			</div>

		<!-- Footer -->
			<div id="footer">
				<div class="container 75%">
					<ul class="icons">
						<li><a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/PabloCianes" class="icon fa-twitter" title="Follow me"><span class="label">Twitter</span></a></li>
						<li><a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/PCianes" class="icon fa-github" title="Fork this site"><span class="label">Github</span></a></li>
						<li><a target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/pablocianes" class="icon fa-facebook" title="Find me in Facebook"><span class="label">Facebook</span></a></li>
					</ul>
					<ul class="copyright">
						<li>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear()  %> <a target="_blank" href="https://pablocianes.com/">Pablo Cianes</a>.</li><li>Design: <a href="http://html5up.net">HTML5 UP</a></li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
	</body>
</html>